\c 6
\s Jehovha anopokana neVaIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Izwai henyu ichi Jehovha chaanoreva: SimukaChinzwai zvino zvinorehwa naJehovha. Simuka, ugorwisana nemakomo, nezvikomo ngazvinzwe izwi rako.
\v 2 Inzwai, imwi makomo, kurwisa kwaJehovha, nemwi nheyo dzenyika dzinogara dziripo; nokuti Jehovha ane kurwisana nevanhu vake, uye achagadzirisana naIsraeri.
\v 3 Haiwa, rudzi rwangu, ndakaitei kwauri: Uye chii chandakakunetesa nacho? Pupura uchindipikisa.
\v 4 Nokuti ndakakukwidzai kubva panyika ye Egipita, ndikakudzikunura kubva paimba yeuranda, ndikatuma pamberi penyu Mozisi naAroni naMiriami.
\v 5 Haiwa, rudzi rwangu, dai warangarira izvo Bharaki mwanakomana waMoabhi zvaakakuraira, neizvo Bharami mwanakomana waBheori zvaakakupindura kwaari, kubva paShitimi kusvika paGirigari, kuti uzive kururama kwa.
\p
\v 6 Ndichauya nei pamberi paJehovha, ndigokotama pamberi paMwari wakakwirira? Ndichauya pamberi pake nezvipo zvinopiswa, uye ndine mhuru dzegore rimwe?
\v 7 Jehovha ungafadzwa here nechuru chemakondohwe, nezvuru gumi zvenzizi dzemafuta? Ndingamuvigira dangwe rangu pachitadzo changu, chibereko chedumbu rangu pachivi chemweya wangu?
\v 8 Wakazivisa kwauri munhu, izvo zvakanaka, zvino Jehovha anodei kwauri kunze kwekuita mutongo, nekuda unyoro, nekufamba mukuzvininipisa pana Mwari wako?
\v 9 Izwi raJehovha rinodanidzira kuguta, neuchenjeri huchaona zita renyu; inzwai shamhu, newakaimisa.
\p
\v 10 Muchine fuma yakaipa muimba yewakaipa here, uye efa yakatapudzwa inonyangadza here?
\v 11 Ndingava wakachena nezviyero zveuipi here, nehomwe yezviyereso zveunyengeri?
\v 12 Nokuti vafumi varo vazere nemhirizhonga, vevagari varo vanotaura nhema, uye rurimi rwavo rwune unyengeri mumuromo wavo.
\v 13 Naizvozvo neni ndicha\add ku\add*rwarisa nekukurova, pakuita dongo nekuda kwezvivi zvako.
\v 14 Iwe uchadya asi haungaguti, uye kupera simba kwako kuchava mukati mako. Zvino uchabvisa, zvino uchabvisa asi haunganunuri, nechauchanunura ndichapa kumunondo.
\v 15 Iwe uchadzvara, asi haungakohwi, uchasvina maorivhi, asi haungazvizodzi mafuta, newaini inotapira asi haunganwi waini.
\v 16 Nokuti zvimiso zvaOmiri zvinochengetwa, nemabasa ese eimba yaAhabhi, uye munofamba mumazano avo, kuti ndikuitei dongo, nevagari varo vave chinhu chinoridzirwa muridzo; saizvozvo muchatakura kushoorwa kwevanhu vangu.